<h1>Kerri Mark Sharp</h1>

<h2><a href="/">/now</a>: <a href="http://kerrisharp.com/now/">kerrisharp.com/now</a></h2>

<h2>Location:</h2>
<p>
Newcastle upon Tyne
England
United Kingdom
</p>

<h2>Professional title:</h2>
<p>
Freelance Graphic & Web Designer at Vestige Media: <a href="http://vestigemedia.com/">http://vestigemedia.com/</a> & Music Industry Virtual Assistant at Stylometric: <a href="http://stylometric.co.uk/">http://stylometric.co.uk/</a>
</p>

<h2>What do you do?</h2>
<p>
I help business owners, entrepreneurs and risk-takers to work more effectively.
</p>

<h2>Why?</h2>
<p>
I am passionate about supporting people to do fantastic work. By helping others to reach their potential, I hope to greatly increase productivity in the world.
</p>

<h2>Recent thought or epiphany?</h2>
<p>
Every day, I think about quitting. I think about getting a ’proper’ job and giving up the dream of financial independence. Yet, I know that success as a business owner doesn’t come overnight. If it did, what would there be to strive for?
</p>

<h2>What should we read?</h2>
<p>
The Freaks Shall Inherit the Earth: Entrepreneurship for Weirdos, Misfits, and World Dominators by Chris Brogan 
</p>

